column5: Awesome 2 Bedrooms, 2 Bathrooms, 2 Car Garage Condo in Brownsville Country Club - Vista Verde Condominiums. Really close to the true commercial center of the city of Brownsville...about 4 blocks from the Sunrise Mall. House trained pets allowed through a small pet fee!
column8: Vista Verde Condo 2/2/2 - Brownsville Country Club
